类 Ramen

  • java.lang.Object
    • Ramen
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Ramen
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is an entity class to represent the state of the buttons(options) in menu that customer to choose The variables in this class will be changed by using the method in ManagementControl class,which done by call the setMethod and getMethod in this Class. Finally the Ramen object will be store or changed in file "Ramen.dat" Other class should use ManagementControl class to understand the state of buttons(options) in menu
    作者:
    Bailin Rong
